Find ways of arranging every RGB color onto a circle, or square, or whatever shape.

Find formular of arrangement.


### tone and brightness circle
- distane to center is brightness. center white. edge black.
- 3 triangelar points of R, G, and B respectively.
- arrange colors from white (left) to black (right)
  - this should become a diamond shape, expand the left/right edge from a point to an edge.

Diamond shape:

        red
              - yellow 
      / green          \
white         - cyan     black
      \ blue           /
              - purple
        red

